#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-04-semeru-scc.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you need to override the auto-detection (for example, to force AppCDS on Semeru for comparison), you can set the type explicitly:"
msgstr "如果需要覆盖自动检测（例如，在 Semeru 上强制使用 AppCDS 进行比较），可以明确设置类型："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-04-semeru-scc.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Valid values are `AUTO` (the default), `AOT`, `AppCDS`, and `SCC`."
msgstr "有效值为 `AUTO` （默认）、 `AOT` 、 `AppCDS` 和 `SCC` 。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-04-semeru-scc.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "One flag, every JVM"
msgstr "一个标志，每个 JVM"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-04-semeru-scc.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This is the design decision we are most proud of in this work. Your build configuration, CI pipeline, and Dockerfile don't need to know which JVM will run the application. Set `quarkus.package.jar.aot.enabled=true`, and the build adapts."
msgstr "这是我们在这项工作中最引以为豪的设计决策。你的构建配置、CI 管道和 Dockerfile 不需要知道哪个 JVM 将运行应用程序。设置 `quarkus.package.jar.aot.enabled=true` ，构建就会适应。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-04-semeru-scc.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This matters in practice. Teams that standardize on Semeru for some services and HotSpot for others can use the same Quarkus build configuration everywhere. Switching JVMs doesn't require touching `application.properties`."
msgstr "这在实践中很重要。如果团队在某些服务上使用 Semeru，而在其他服务上使用 HotSpot，就可以在所有地方使用相同的 Quarkus 构建配置。切换 JVM 不需要触动 `application.properties` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-04-semeru-scc.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It also means that the Quarkus documentation, guides, and examples work the same way regardless of the JVM.\n"
"When we write \"enable AOT for faster startup,\" that statement is true whether you run HotSpot, Semeru, or an older JDK."
msgstr "这也意味着，无论使用哪种 JVM，Quarkus 文档、指南和示例的工作方式都是一样的。当我们写到 \"启用 AOT 以加快启动速度 \"时，无论您运行的是 HotSpot、Semeru 还是旧版 JDK，这句话都是正确的。"

